# Auth & sessions

Read **`docs/agents/auth.md`** before non-trivial changes.

- Better Auth + SQLite `data/auth.db`; Keycloak provider id **`keycloak`**.
- Route handler: `app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts`; gate: `middleware.ts` → `/sign-in`.
- APIs: `requireApiSession()` in `lib/require-session.ts`.
- Edit/delete authorization: `lib/session-roles.ts` — owner email or Keycloak role **`role_admin`**.
- Redirect URI in Keycloak: `{BETTER_AUTH_URL}/api/auth/oauth2/callback/keycloak`.
- After schema changes: `npx @better-auth/cli@latest migrate --config lib/auth.ts --yes`.

Update **`AGENTS.md`**, **`docs/agents/auth.md`**, and **`README.md`** if env or redirect contracts change.
